<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charSet="utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=5, user-scalable=yes"/><link rel="stylesheet" href="/_next/static/css/ab47ee2ccd2cf533.css" data-precedence="next"/><link rel="stylesheet" href="/_next/static/css/edd663882f728b38.css" data-precedence="next"/><link rel="stylesheet" href="/_next/static/css/bdbf173f49cc9fe0.css" data-precedence="next"/><link rel="preload" as="script" fetchPriority="low" href="/_next/static/chunks/webpack-299ce91af42ed7ee.js"/><script src="/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-fbb669b6c51e2ad7.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/93794-6ce4a95cc576c155.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/main-app-395ad559cef0ac68.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/9da6db1e-889f60c7db26922c.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/18409-46308ee79addd19b.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/66609-1fef72a9b9d9f9b5.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/49541-02f2977f368e19d7.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/9683-8520c627689e1a1e.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/36376-3f59d0495b0fe29b.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/39989-4e1d9e637092a2e6.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/32874-c0041ee62723ace1.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/95116-0588a7c2bf497f41.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-4879f9ea25d65f4f.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/98500-1494f211297c269f.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/app/error-b3db3e44aa34a133.js" async=""></script><script src="https://clerk.avocadoai.co/npm/@clerk/clerk-js@5/dist/clerk.browser.js" data-clerk-js-script="true" async="" crossorigin="anonymous" data-clerk-publishable-key="pk_live_Y2xlcmsuYXZvY2Fkb2FpLmNvJA"></script><link rel="preload" href="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-B0ZNSHXVGH" as="script"/><link rel="preload" href="https://datafa.st/js/script.js" as="script"/><meta name="next-size-adjust" content=""/><meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)"/><meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0a0a" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)"/><title>Avocado | AI Video Ads</title><meta name="description" content="Avocado AI is the all-in-one AI creative workspace. Generate professional images, videos, UGC ads, music, and voice content powered by 87+ world-class AI models. No agencies. No watermarks."/><meta name="author" content="Avocado AI Team"/><link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest"/><meta name="keywords" content="avocado ai,avocadoai,ai creative studio,all in one ai creative platform,ai content creation platform,ai creative workspace,ai ad generator,ai creative tools for brands,ai tools for creators,no watermark ai generator,full commercial rights ai,ai content for tiktok instagram youtube shopify,midjourney alternative,midjourney alternative free,canva ai alternative,canva ai video generator alternative"/><meta name="creator" content="Avocado AI"/><meta name="publisher" content="Avocado AI"/><meta name="robots" content="index, follow"/><meta name="googlebot" content="index, follow, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-snippet:-1"/><link rel="canonical" href="https://www.avocadoai.co"/><meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no, address=no, email=no"/><meta name="google-site-verification" content="npFyloQ2uqU2y7Jb-av-860CRw0laD34avv1CUvjm1M"/><meta property="og:title" content="Avocado | AI Video Ads"/><meta property="og:description" content="Generate studio-quality images, video ads &amp; AI voiceovers in seconds."/><meta property="og:url" content="https://www.avocadoai.co"/><meta property="og:site_name" content="Avocado AI"/><meta property="og:locale" content="en_US"/><meta property="og:image" content="https://www.avocadoai.co/assets/og-image.png"/><meta property="og:image:width" content="1200"/><meta property="og:image:height" content="630"/><meta property="og:image:alt" content="Avocado | AI Video Ads"/><meta property="og:type" content="website"/><meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"/><meta name="twitter:site" content="@avocado_ai"/><meta name="twitter:creator" content="@avocado_ai"/><meta name="twitter:title" content="Avocado | AI Video Ads"/><meta name="twitter:description" content="Generate studio-quality images, video ads &amp; AI voiceovers in seconds."/><meta name="twitter:image" content="https://www.avocadoai.co/assets/og-image.png"/><link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon-16x16.png"/><link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico"/><link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/apple-touch-icon.png"/><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Organization","name":"Avocado AI","url":"https://www.avocadoai.co","logo":"https://www.avocadoai.co/assets/og-image.png","sameAs":["https://twitter.com/avocado_ai"]}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"WebSite","name":"Avocado AI","url":"https://www.avocadoai.co","potentialAction":{"@type":"SearchAction","target":"https://www.avocadoai.co/?q={search_term_string}","query-input":"required name=search_term_string"}}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"SoftwareApplication","name":"Avocado AI","description":"All-in-one AI creative workspace for generating images, videos, UGC ads, music, and voice content. Powered by 87+ world-class AI models.","applicationCategory":"MultimediaApplication","operatingSystem":"Web","url":"https://www.avocadoai.co","offers":{"@type":"AggregateOffer","lowPrice":"19.99","highPrice":"249","priceCurrency":"EUR","offerCount":"5"}}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is Avocado AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Avocado AI is an all-in-one creative platform that replaces 5+ separate tools. Generate professional-quality videos (22+ models including Sora 2 Pro & Veo 3), images (19+ models), music, voiceovers, and AI UGC — all in one workspace. It includes Storyboards with an infinite canvas for planning campaigns, real-time team collaboration, and Lini, your AI creative director."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do the plans and pricing work?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Avocado AI uses a credit-based system. Plans start at €19.99/month (Intro, 75 credits) and go up to €249/month (Pro, 2,000 credits). Different AI models consume different amounts of credits based on their complexity, and you always see the exact cost before generating. Credits reset each month, and you can upgrade, downgrade, or cancel anytime. All plans include commercial rights and no watermarks."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What are the commercial usage rights?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"All content generated with Avocado AI comes with full commercial usage rights. Use your generated images, videos, music, and voiceovers in ads, social media, client work, websites, and any commercial project — without watermarks. Your content is yours to use commercially, even after your subscription ends."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What is Lini AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Lini is your AI creative director inside Avocado. Tell Lini what you need — describe your campaign, product, or idea in plain language — and Lini orchestrates the right AI models to generate images, videos, music, and more. It's like having a creative assistant that understands your brand and handles the technical work. Lini is available on Starter plans and above."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What are Storyboards and the Infinite Canvas?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Storyboards are Avocado's unique visual planning tool: an infinite canvas where you can arrange, compare, and iterate on all your creative assets side by side. Plan ad sequences, map out social campaigns, and manage video series with drag-and-drop scenes. Invite your team to collaborate in real-time."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What can I create with Avocado AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"AI videos for TikTok, YouTube, and ads. Product photography and marketing images. AI UGC with realistic avatars. Background music and sound effects. Voiceovers in 29+ languages. Visual storyboards for campaign planning. Everything you need for social media, e-commerce, and client work — created in minutes, not days."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Why pay for 5 subscriptions when Avocado replaces them all?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Avocado AI replaces Midjourney ($30/mo), ElevenLabs ($22/mo), Suno ($10/mo), Runway ($28/mo), and Canva ($15/mo) — that's $105+/month with 5 separate logins, 5 learning curves, and no unified workflow. Avocado starts at €19.99/month with all tools in one workspace, one credit system, and full commercial rights."}}]}</script><meta name="robots" content="noindex"/><script src="/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js" noModule=""></script></head><body class="__variable_f367f3 __variable_dd5b2f __variable_46b04e __className_f367f3 min-h-screen bg-background antialiased"><div hidden=""><!--$--><!--/$--></div><script>((a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h)=>{let i=document.documentElement,j=["light","dark"];function k(b){var c;(Array.isArray(a)?a:[a]).forEach(a=>{let c="class"===a,d=c&&f?e.map(a=>f[a]||a):e;c?(i.classList.remove(...d),i.classList.add(f&&f[b]?f[b]:b)):i.setAttribute(a,b)}),c=b,h&&j.includes(c)&&(i.style.colorScheme=c)}if(d)k(d);else try{let a=localStorage.getItem(b)||c,d=g&&"system"===a?window.matchMedia("(prefers-color-scheme: dark)").matches?"dark":"light":a;k(d)}catch(a){}})("class","theme","system",null,["light","dark"],null,true,true)</script><!--$!--><template data-dgst="NEXT_HTTP_ERROR_FALLB